NFRArchitectureEvalutionSimpleQuantificationTool  simple tool used to quantify the Nonfunctional requirements necessary  for evaluation of  software architecture. The user of this  tool can be anyone  who wishes to use  measure and quantify  functional parameters  along with  tradeoff factors for a software architecture in terms of security, performance, reliability, scalability, availability and any other nfr parameter that you wish to add in the Process.
